<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_150" id="75r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_150_r2l1">Burkharten hofner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_150_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Burkhart / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des kümman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l3">hüllfroſchs wegen / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l4">euch vviſſen / <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> derſelb ~ hülfroſch in den nehſten Acht <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l5">cʒu vns herein 
<del rend="strikethrough">kum </del> gen <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> kümt / So ſol Er cʒwen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l7">tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_150_r2l6">hie </ab></add> ein ſleht geleit 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu vns bey vns vnd für </del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l8">cʒu vns vnd von vns für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ongeuerde / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l9">vnd ſo wöllen vvir ſein rede 
